{"tid":224992,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本網站針對500名20至40歲調查最想擁有臉蛋 新垣結衣勉強擠身前四","createTime":"2017-05-01T12:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T04:17:22.000Z","uid":9573,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4744e706a5dccf029a78983acffba2f2f1d5086c","tid":224992,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:50:45.000Z","msg":"經濟學家Daniel S. Hamermesh曾指出，美人與非美人在生涯中所獲得的財產，大概能有日幣2700萬元（約台幣739萬元）的差距，讓許多女性聽了都直呼：「想要變美女！」而日本網站《美レンジャー》近日也針對500名20至40歲的女性作調查，票選出時下日本女性最想擁有的臉蛋，第一名遠遠勝過其他候補者！<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2491/d2491481.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2491%2Fd2491481.jpg&h=b980badd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲日本網站票選出2017年女性最想擁有的臉蛋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z58887a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz58887a.jpg&h=da09a66b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲朱千雪子經常是選美投票的冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n「女性最想擁有的臉蛋」冠軍由人妻北川景子拿下，12%的投票率遠遠勝過眾女星。北川的五官深邃、比例分配勻稱，而且又是瓜子臉，相當符合美女標準，尤其是她的性感豐唇，從出道以來就一直是被討論的焦點，連女網友都感嘆地說：「如果能變成朱千雪子，第一件要做的事就是從早到晚都在外面晃！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h16wu24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh16wu24.jpg&h=0df83ef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱千雪子、石原聰美2位公認的美女則分別以8.8%、8.6%得票率榮獲二、三名；而「國民老婆」新垣結衣以8.4%緊追在後。第五到十名還有佐佐木希美、Rola、柴崎幸、宮崎葵、堀北真希、綾瀨遙、長澤雅美、廣瀨鈴等人。"},{"pid":"245654c544922e34f4a646f10bfbc68127501654","tid":224992,"uid":71330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:54:20.000Z","msg":"認真第3名係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3250fc464a5ae4dad73adb3bd7ca5ad6d55e27c0","tid":224992,"uid":12269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:56:01.000Z","msg":"女性角度同男性角度真係睇得好唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcaa0aeb75f30e720f2049d4026f7fb9e1fdd5f9","tid":224992,"uid":2022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:07:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b2ebd334128fa38811595dd26cb0914a459fb17","tid":224992,"uid":3748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:12:46.000Z","msg":"堀北真希<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91a239eb17dc824e37d2c80e25fa3095d228270","tid":224992,"uid":6955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:21:31.000Z","msg":"今次睇咗user name先入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54782364df0d4167ed8f7a55392e898a3b61de35","tid":224992,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:45:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>堀北真希<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61a1e9f39e0d2ea8fea0cbf071adb748eebc7a1","tid":224992,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T01:47:00.000Z","msg":"其實呢d樣真係好一般<br />\n<br />\n北京出差一轉，見到唔少樣，屌打呢d女"},{"pid":"da0c6d9e44cfd03c725c7c36549251b8929485d2","tid":224992,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T02:09:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實呢d樣真係好一般<br />\n<br />\n北京出差一轉，見到唔少樣，屌打呢d女</blockquote><br />\n睇撚小強國整容風氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db08e8ee703b4ada61525ff6ce55436b1bf85f4","tid":224992,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T02:12:51.000Z","msg":"朱千雪子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17859b13f6de3a62750fa05516